            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="#191919"><path d="M13.54 12a6.8 6.8 0 01-6.77 6.82A6.8 6.8 0 010 12a6.8 6.8 0 016.77-6.82A6.8 6.8 0 0113.54 12zM20.96 12c0 3.54-1.51 6.42-3.38 6.42-1.87 0-3.39-2.88-3.39-6.42s1.52-6.42 3.39-6.42S20.96 8.46 20.96 12zM24 12c0 3.17-.53 5.75-1.19 5.75-.66 0-1.19-2.58-1.19-5.75s.53-5.75 1.19-5.75C23.47 6.25 24 8.83 24 12z"/></svg>
